  <T n="entry_text">0x321EECBF<!--String: "Vegetation and Old Firewatch Tower"--></T>
  <V n="entry_text_description" t="enabled">
    <T n="enabled">0x3B3D1204<!--String: "The abundant woods in Wanderwood Wilds are the result of the Great Wave sweeping through Gibbi Point, leaving the soil more fertile and, well, more inclined towards helping a lot of trees and plants to grow. Sims used to get horribly lost in the vegetation and frequent lava flows would cause fires in the area, necessitating the creation of the Old Firewatch Tower to help keep an eye on things. These days, things are a little calmer though you'll still want to keep your bearings while navigating around."--></T>
  </V>
